cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper introduces two artificial datasets for testing the learning ability of video processing systems. The datasets involve goal-oriented tasks and are meant to assess the sanity of deep neural network models that aim to encode, reconstruct or predict video frame sequences. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV), Robotics (cs.RO), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), or Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories.
